# GOSE baked default app set — the locked §4 set (docs/25, Zeke 2026-06-06).
# One Flathub flatpak application id per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# provision-baked-apps.sh installs every id here that is missing (idempotent), so a
# fresh image / factory reset always lands with the full default set installed.
# Keep this in sync with docs/25 §4 and gose_vm_server._STORE.
#
# id                         # role
com.valvesoftware.Steam       # Steam — baked in (Zeke's call), not a store download
org.mozilla.firefox           # Firefox — THE default web browser (human's)
org.chromium.Chromium         # Chromium — kept alongside Firefox (agent-side browser)
org.videolan.VLC              # VLC — media playback, plays ~everything
md.obsidian.Obsidian          # Obsidian — notes / knowledge vault (Zeke's standard)
